reviewText:
For those who like B-Rate films & also like Full Moon Entertainment films, this is another score.  This is a great 3 DVD set.
  1) Bleed- A girfriend believes her boyfriend & his friends about having a "Murder Club"
  2) Intruder- A Supermarket is about ready to go out of business.  But the night crew starts mysteriously dying.
  3) Cut Throat- A crew of a low budget horror film starts to die off
  Overall, you can't go wrong with this set
